cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper deals with multi-view image clustering, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The proposed method involves joint learning of self-representation and indicator, which is a common approach in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves fusion of multiple views, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
